snippet.title: Rust Console Edition - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
In Rust, there is one goal above everything else: survive. Conquer thirst and hunger, battle the elements, create clothing and stay safe against hostile forces including other players, scientists, bears, wolves or even succumb to fire, drowning or radiation poisoning. A game without rules, Rust doesn’t tell its inhabitants what to do. 

Rust Console Edition is available now on PlayStation 4! 

Rated Mature: Violence, Blood, In-Game Purchases, Users Interact
